        lesson 4

        FOLDER STRUCTURE

              1       tsconfig.json
                       - basic typescript settings

            2       src
                      -app module
                          -app component 
                              -app.component.html   -> html code
                              -app.component.scss   -> style sheet
                              -app.component.spec.ts  -> unit test script
                              - app.component.ts  -> class file
               

               3)  assets
                     -images
                     -mock data
                     -apis


                4)  environments

                     -dev
                     -local
                     -prodection

                     

                 5) index.html
                       single page application
                         
                         dynamicaly data get injected into index.html

                         <app-root>  - code injected at run time




                  6)   main.ts

                        --bootstrap module -- it means when application starts it will see main.ts which module to boot

                              
                              -- appModule

                              -- starting point of your application


                               -- default appmodule will start
                                
                                -- we can also can change the module when necessory

                                --No mandatory it should be in appmodule we can change it





                         7) polyfills.ts

                               --  supporting older browsers


                          8) styles.css
                                --global stylesheet for global





                          9) test.ts

                             --test scripts for the main.ts file
                             
                               
                                 





                          






   